X:13
T:XIII - Hand Interchange
C:Rodriguez Do Campo Method (2020)
M:3/4
L:1/8
Q:1/4=72
K:C
%%text Seamless hand switching. LH plays 4 notes, RH continues 4 notes.
%%text Must sound like one continuous scale. Also practice as plaque chords.
%%text LH(MI): 4-3-2-1, RH(MD): 1-2-3-4. Apply all permutations.
V:1 clef=treble name="RH"
z4 EF|GABc z2|z4 ef|gabc' z2|z4 e'f'|g'a'b'c'' z2|c''6|]
V:2 clef=bass name="LH"
!accent!C,D,E,F, z2|z4 !accent!CD|!accent!EFGAz2|z4 !accent!cd|!accent!efga z2|z6|z6|]
